{"tid":1620603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"施永青：「悲劇遲早會發生」","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T15:48:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ff730627d7964012ba7294f948103f46ba0a7ccb","tid":1620603,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:51:29.000Z","msg":"政府將於午夜起推禁蒙面法，中原集團主席施永青認為，早前形勢已預視到政府會引用《緊急法》處理事件，現今事情正高速發展，若雙方不降低武力手段，悲刻遲早會發生，但各方都有責任，應該克制，降低暴力。<br />\n<br />\n對於後市看法，施永青認為政治事情影響整個市場，無一例外， 惟樓市不像股市般情緒化，而局勢動盪下，投資意欲低迷，而現時樓市未出現崩潰性下跌及拋售情況，雖然目前換樓活動減少，但仍有自住需求；樂觀態度來看，當樓價下跌約10%時，開始見到有承接力，亦預料未來樓市將緩緩下跌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1570182538872&amp;issue=20191004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1570182538872%26issue%3D20191004&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJG73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=f8875881\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1570182538872%26issue%3D20191004&h=35019890\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1570182538872&amp;issue=20191004</a>"},{"pid":"c650bf9e5531cc7ebd36f72b3be3b1593a1ec698","tid":1620603,"uid":17130,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦 聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"6ffbe81c7d7eb989786e69fd6b84333acc74ec20","tid":1620603,"uid":997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"仲諗樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05599694ea739edd19ba747f9f1a47c560449280","tid":1620603,"uid":113922,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"仲掛住d樓，聖誕快樂啦，屌你老母"},{"pid":"e2a84ed0c040b6d3a5737d69548be717321343b3","tid":1620603,"uid":36158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"9e5c55bb6f1ae4e3215ff54c7f9c31bdba33cae4","tid":1620603,"u